Messerschmitt-Boelkow-Boehm G.B.B.

H.P.P.Senate formal endorsement of a merger with DaimlerBenz AG until another meeting for Nov. 17

Di owners of di defence, aerospace engineering, wey include three regional states, several industrial companies and banks, meet Friday to talk on top di matter, wey be sey DaimlerBenz go get 50.01% of wetin dem dey sell for di market.

But aparentity no fit reach dem because of opposition from Hamburg, and Bremen wey dey demand more power for di German Airbus operation, and better guarantee for job loss wey dey Northern Germany.

Di two states and di state of Bavaria still hold majority for MBB, but dia stake go fall around 30% after DaimlerBenz take over di matter.

